[['MarketResearch.get_market_share', {'name': 'MarketResearch.get_market_share', 'description': 'Get the market share data for a specific company and its competitors', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'company', 'description': 'the name of the company', 'type': 'STRING'}, {'name': 'competitors', 'description': 'list of competitor names', 'type': 'LIST'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'market_share', 'description': 'market share percentage of the company'}, {'name': 'competitor_shares', 'description': 'market share percentages of competitors'}]}],
['MarketResearch.analyze_revenue', {'name': 'MarketResearch.analyze_revenue', 'description': 'Analyze the revenue data for a specific company', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'company', 'description': 'the name of the company', 'type': 'STRING'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'revenue', 'description': 'total revenue of the company'}]}],
['MarketResearch.analyze_customer_count', {'name': 'MarketResearch.analyze_customer_count', 'description': 'Analyze the customer count data for a specific company', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'company', 'description': 'the name of the company', 'type': 'STRING'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'customer_count', 'description': 'total number of customers'}]}],
['MarketResearch.evaluate_market_position', {'name': 'MarketResearch.evaluate_market_position', 'description': 'Evaluate the market position of a specific company using a market position model', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'company', 'description': 'the name of the company', 'type': 'STRING'}, {'name': 'market_share', 'description': 'market share data', 'type': 'STRING'}, {'name': 'revenue', 'description': 'revenue data', 'type': 'STRING'}, {'name': 'customer_count', 'description': 'customer count data', 'type': 'STRING'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'market_position', 'description': 'evaluated market position of the company'}]}],
['MarketResearch.generate_report', {'name': 'MarketResearch.generate_report', 'description': 'Generate a market position report based on the evaluated market position', 'required_parameters': [{'name': 'company', 'description': 'the name of the company', 'type': 'STRING'}, {'name': 'market_position', 'description': 'evaluated market position data', 'type': 'STRING'}], 'optional_parameters': [], 'return_data': [{'name': 'report', 'description': 'generated market position report'}]}]]
请生成一个解决用户问题的计划，计划应该是一个行为列表，每个行为的格式如下:

[{
    // 动作的ID
    "id": number;
    // 动作要调用的API名称
    "name": string;
    // 当前API的参数输入(JSON格式)
    "args": "str(Record<string, any>)";
}, ...
]

你可以在计划中想象参数的值，这些指令将按顺序执行。
例如，如果你想调用 `api1` 并传入 `arg1` 和 `arg2`，你可以写下面的计划:

[{
    "id": 0,
    "name": "api1",
    "args": "{'arg1': 'value1', 'arg2': 'value2', ...}",
}, ...
]

这些参数将在执行时被替换为真实的值。请注意，参数应该是一个字符串，而不是一个字典。
请在字典的参数中使用 ''，在其他地方使用 ""，不要打印值为 None 或 null 的参数。

你应该只生成一个 JSON 格式的计划列表。列表应该是完整的计划列表，不要有 `...`。
不要生成任何解释 JSON 的文本。

